@DATABASE "Pinball"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - P - Pinball"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - P
                   ====================================

                                  Pinball
                                  =======



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(31566,0)"}          31566,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28950,255)"}          28950,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This game seems to crash a bit on the Emulator.

                         Rastan
@endnode
